OL,3,CNurses in Wales 'incensed' over pay
OL,4,Coffer to doctors
OL,6,FThe Royal College of Nursing (RCN) in
OL,7,FWales has hit out at a new pay offer
OL,8,Fput to doctors.
OL,10,FHelen Whyley, the union's Executive
OL,11,FDirector said her members feel "let
OL,12,Fdown and misled by this government"
OL,13,Fafter nurses accepted a 5% pay deal in
OL,14,FSeptember.
OL,16,FShe continued: "the repeated firm
OL,17,Fposition from the Welsh Government
OL,18,Fthat there was no money in the pot for
OL,19,FNHS nursing staff salaries was either
OL,20,Funtrue or demonstrates that they can't
OL,21,Fmanage their finances.
