OL,6,F"Either way it shows a total disregard
OL,7,Fto principle of equity of approach to
OL,8,FNHS negotiations."
OL,10,FCriticising the First Minister, Ms
OL,11,FWhyley said "his government have
OL,12,Ffailed to fulfil the promises made to
OL,13,Fnurses in last year's pay award and
OL,14,Fnow they add insult to that injury by
OL,15,Fsubstantially increasing only the
OL,16,Fdoctors' pay award for 2023-24."
