OL,6,FThe pay deal for junior doctors,
OL,7,Fconsultants and specialist doctors has
OL,8,Frisen from the original offer put on
OL,9,Fthe table of 5%, which was described
OL,10,Fas the worst in the UK.
OL,12,FA vote will soon take place on whether
OL,13,Fjunior doctors will accept a 12.4%
OL,14,Fuplift, consultants a rise of up to
OL,15,F10.1% and specialist doctors an
OL,16,Fincrease between 6.1%-9.2%.
