OL,6,FIn September 2023, nurses voted to
OL,7,Faccept an offer which included a 5%
OL,8,Fpay rise for 2023-2024 and a one-off
OL,9,Fpayment for 2022-2023. There was also
OL,10,Fa promise to improve working
OL,11,Fconditions.
OL,13,FIt brought an end to months of strike
OL,14,Faction which began in December 2022
OL,15,Fand lasted until June 2023.
