OL,6,FAnd in the last week, the union said
OL,7,Fpatients are experiencing "absolutely
OL,8,Fshocking" conditions being treated in
OL,9,Fhospital corridors in Wales.
OL,11,FThe Chair of RCN Wales said nearly
OL,12,Fhalf of their members had told the
OL,13,Funion they intend to leave the
OL,14,Fprofession.
OL,16,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,17,F"We greatly value Wales' nursing
OL,18,Fworkforce, which does so much to look
OL,19,Fafter and provide life-saving and life-
OL,20,Fchanging care for people, often in
OL,21,Fvery pressured circumstances.
